change big banner

in terminal follow this commands,
$sudo apt-get install figlet
$figlet Banner name

after your customize banner name will generate copy that banner name and open rugged-board

in root terminal follow this cmds

~#cd /etc
~#vim issue     in this remove old-banner and place new-banner which copied from termial and save it.
~#cd ssh
~#vim sshd_config   in this remove # and none, like (#Banner none)- only Banner should be there after save it.
boot the board

Note:This is only for sd card 
